{
  "texts": [
    "The second salient issue necessitates acknowledging that the evaluation type may influence students' fairness perceptions.",
    "However, we did not consider it a variable but rather a research context.",
    "This decision was predicated on several key reasons.",
    "Primarily, our focus was on students' fairness perceptions, not the evaluations themselves.",
    "Consequently, we sought to measure students' fairness perceptions across different contexts to isolate the impact of assessment contexts on fairness perceptions."
  ]
}